{
  "texts": [
    "To mitigate the learning curve and customization efforts, existing platforms, such as Character.AI and Poe, have offered rich lists of pre-created personas [15,73] and customization options (e.g., demographics, personality keywords) [37].",
    "However, people may be inclined to select from the available options rather than exploring their own ideas.",
    "To facilitate LLM customization reflecting individuals' desired outputs without constraints, we need to carefully balance the amount of guidance to provide and user autonomy.",
    "This involves offering supportive resources, such as hints, examples, and prompt editing support, while encouraging people to express their unique needs and preferences.",
    "DR2:Expanding customization possibilities to enrich user experience."
  ]
}